PS: ProMED is an international infectious disease community. Made up of researchers, academics, public health workers, clinical medicine practitioners, and many others, our community is united by a common goal to prevent disease and treat it when it happens. Community works. A coordinated global approach, international cooperation and honesty, and political will helped to contain the SARS epidemic in a period of 8 months. Please join over 1300 colleagues who have demonstrated just how important they think the ProMED-mail community is in achieving our goal! Please give now.

